  npcName: Grieving Monk
  npcSprite: {fileID: 0}
  dialogue:
  - You... you have done it. The darkness has lifted. I can feel their souls at peace.
  - Thank you. You have given an old monk his only wish.
  - Take this sacred charm. It carries the strength of every monk who wore it before
    you.
  - You will need it. I sense a great battle ahead of you.
